### Script Organization
- **All utility scripts** should be placed in `/scripts/` directory
- **Test scripts** should be placed in `/scripts/tests/` directory (if created)
- **Build scripts** (post_build.sh, build.sh, bump_version.py) belong in `/scripts/`
- **Main project scripts** (generate_and_open_xcode.sh, init_plugin_project.sh, dependencies.sh) belong in project root
